        h1 Oh Hai There!

         h3 Welcome to PubSeq!

         p PubSeq is sequence-based search engine for MEDLINE abstracts (a.k.a. 'PUBMED abstracts').

         h3 Pub... what?
         
         p PubSeq enables researcher to search the whole (yes, all of them -- well until they get indexed at least!) MEDLINE corpus by sequence alone. To use PubSeq, simply write in the sequence of protein you are interested in and PubSeq will return to you with the list of articles mentioning it. Simple as that!

